In [11]:
smt = SMOTE(X,y,K=5,dup_size=1)
smt_X = np.vstack((X,smt))
smt_y = np.concatenate((y,np.ones(smt.shape[0])))

model = RandomForestClassifier(max_depth=10, random_state=0)
model.fit(smt_X, smt_y)
decision_plot(smt_X,smt_y,model)
